@startuml IBM_customer-sentiment-on-seller-quality-nlu-cp4d

actor User
participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook
database "Db2 Database" as DB2
participant "Watson NLU" as NLU
participant "Embedded Dashboard" as Dashboard

User -> Notebook: Execute notebook
activate Notebook

Notebook -> DB2: Connect and fetch data
activate DB2
DB2 --> Notebook: Return customer review data
deactivate DB2

loop For each review
    Notebook -> NLU: Send review text for analysis
    activate NLU
    NLU --> Notebook: Return sentiment and emotion scores
    deactivate NLU
end

Notebook -> Notebook: Calculate seller ratings

Notebook -> DB2: Store processed data
activate DB2
DB2 --> Notebook: Confirm data storage
deactivate DB2

Notebook -> Dashboard: Update visualization data
activate Dashboard
Dashboard --> Notebook: Confirm update
deactivate Dashboard

Notebook --> User: Display results
deactivate Notebook

User -> Dashboard: Interact with dashboard
activate Dashboard
Dashboard --> User: Show interactive visualizations
deactivate Dashboard

@enduml